# NLA Historical Archive: Krückeberg Records

Welcome to the digital archive of the Krückeberg family and related archival records from the *Staatsarchiv Bückeburg*. 

This project documents the transliteration and analysis of historical *Kurrentschrift* and *Fraktur* documents.

